ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of IAN C. SWAN of Lake of The Woods, Nova Scotia, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective April 26, 2007, in the place of Terence Pittman.
